First City Monument Bank’s First-Half Net Income Rises

-- B y   E m e l e   O n u
-- 
2011-07-22T13:25:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-22/first-city-monument-bank-s-first-half-net-income-rises-correct-.html
(Corrects company’s name in headline.)  First City Monument Bank Plc (FCMB) ’s
first-half profit rose 89 percent, the Lagos-based lender said
today in an e-mailed statement.  Net income jumped to 5.3 billion naira in the six months
through June, from 2.8 billion naira a year earlier. Revenue
climbed to 35 billion naira, from 30 billion naira, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emele Onu in Lagos at 
 eonu1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
